    <h1>Best Protein Tracking App <span>for Men Over 40</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Most tracking apps were built for 25-year-olds counting every macro. Here's what actually works when your goal shifts from bulking to keeping what you've built.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:1rem; font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--green-dark);">Most men over 40 aren't low on effort — they're low on protein.</p>
  </header>

